\f1\b\fs36 \cf0 \strokec2 INPUT CONTEXT\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 You may be given:\uc0\u8232 \'95 App description and goals\u8232 \'95 Existing features and flows\u8232 \'95 Data models or AI capabilities\u8232 \'95 Screens, routes, or components\u8232 \'95 Constraints (technical, ethical, or business)\
