\f1\b\fs36 \cf0 \strokec2 YOUR TASKS\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

\fs28 \cf0 1. Latent Capability Audit\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 Examine what the app already has access to (data, inputs, models, actions, signals).\
Ask:\uc0\u8232 \'95 What does the app 
\f2\i \strokec2 know
\f0\i0 \strokec2  that it is not using?\uc0\u8232 \'95 What patterns could be inferred but are not?\u8232 \'95 What is being collected but not reflected back to the user?\u8232 \'95 What intelligence is trapped in raw data?\
Surface:\uc0\u8232 \'95 Insights that could be generated automatically\u8232 \'95 Summaries, scores, trends, or predictions not yet exposed\u8232 \'95 Derived value from existing inputs\u8232 \'95 Opportunities for \'93this app already knows this, so why doesn\'92t it say it?\'94\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \strokec3 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

\f1\b\fs28 \cf0 \strokec2 2. Unfinished Feature Potential\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 For every existing feature or workflow:\
Ask:\uc0\u8232 \'95 What is the \'93next obvious step\'94 the app does not take?\u8232 \'95 Where does the app stop one move too early?\u8232 \'95 What manual work is still being asked of the user?\u8232 \'95 What decision is left unsupported?\
Surface:\uc0\u8232 \'95 Auto-completions, suggestions, or continuations\u8232 \'95 Follow-up actions the app could initiate\u8232 \'95 Smart defaults or recommendations\u8232 \'95 \'93Assist me\'94 moments where AI should step in\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \strokec3 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

\f1\b\fs28 \cf0 \strokec2 3. Cross-Feature Synthesis\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 Look for places where features exist in parallel but do not talk to each other.\
Ask:\uc0\u8232 \'95 What features should inform each other but don\'92t?\u8232 \'95 What data from Feature A could enhance Feature B?\u8232 \'95 Where could the app feel more \'93aware\'94 of itself?\
Surface:\uc0\u8232 \'95 Feature combinations that unlock new value\u8232 \'95 Shared intelligence layers\u8232 \'95 Moments where the app could feel cohesive instead of modular\u8232 \'95 Opportunities for orchestration rather than isolation\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \strokec3 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

\f1\b\fs28 \cf0 \strokec2 4. User Leverage & Power Ups\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 Evaluate how much work the user is doing vs. how much the app is doing.\
Ask:\uc0\u8232 \'95 Where is the user doing expert-level reasoning manually?\u8232 \'95 Where could the app act as a multiplier?\u8232 \'95 Where could effort be reduced without loss of control?\
Surface:\uc0\u8232 \'95 Power-user features hidden behind simple UIs\u8232 \'95 Progressive enhancement ideas\u8232 \'95 Optional \'93advanced\'94 layers\u8232 \'95 Ways to make users feel smarter, faster, or calmer\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \strokec3 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

\f1\b\fs28 \cf0 \strokec2 5. Differentiation & Competitive Blind Spots\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 Without naming competitors explicitly:\
Ask:\uc0\u8232 \'95 What category conventions is this app blindly following?\u8232 \'95 Where could it deliberately break pattern?\u8232 \'95 What user pain is assumed but not solved?\
Surface:\uc0\u8232 \'95 Unexpected but aligned features\u8232 \'95 Emotional differentiators (trust, relief, confidence, clarity)\u8232 \'95 Features that signal \'93this app gets me\'94\u8232 \'95 Category re-framings\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \strokec3 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

\f1\b\fs28 \cf0 \strokec2 6. AI-Native Opportunity Audit\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 Specifically evaluate AI usage:\
Ask:\uc0\u8232 \'95 Is AI being used as a tool or as a collaborator?\u8232 \'95 Where is AI reactive instead of proactive?\u8232 \'95 Where could AI notice things the user didn\'92t ask about?\
Surface:\uc0\u8232 \'95 Proactive alerts or nudges\u8232 \'95 Pattern detection and anomaly spotting\u8232 \'95 Context-aware suggestions\u8232 \'95 AI-generated next steps, not just answers\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \strokec3 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

\f1\b\fs28 \cf0 \strokec2 7. Monetization & Value Exchange Opportunities\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 Evaluate the value surface:\
Ask:\uc0\u8232 \'95 Where is the app creating value that is not captured?\u8232 \'95 What would users reasonably pay for more of?\u8232 \'95 What feels premium but is currently free?\
Surface:\uc0\u8232 \'95 Natural upgrade paths\u8232 \'95 Paid enhancements that feel fair, not extractive\u8232 \'95 Bundles, tiers, or add-ons aligned with real value\u8232 \'95 Enterprise or team-level leverage points\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \strokec3 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

\f1\b\fs28 \cf0 \strokec2 8. Ecosystem & Reuse Opportunities\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 Zoom out.\
Ask:\uc0\u8232 \'95 What parts of this app could be reused elsewhere?\u8232 \'95 What could become a shared service, API, or module?\u8232 \'95 What internal tools could become external features?\
Surface:\uc0\u8232 \'95 Platform-level thinking\u8232 \'95 Cross-product leverage\u8232 \'95 Internal abstractions worth formalizing\u8232 \'95 Future-proofing moves\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \strokec3 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

\f1\b\fs28 \cf0 \strokec2 9. \'93Unknown Unknowns\'94 Prompting\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 Finally, step beyond explicit logic.\
Ask:\uc0\u8232 \'95 What assumptions does this app make about its users?\u8232 \'95 What if those assumptions are wrong?\u8232 \'95 What user story is not being told?\
Surface:\uc0\u8232 \'95 Edge cases worth embracing\u8232 \'95 Non-obvious user types\u8232 \'95 Alternate modes of use\u8232 \'95 Features that feel risky but visionary\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \strokec3 \
